### Banking API - Exemplos de Uso HTTP
### Base URL: https://localhost:7085 (HTTPS) ou http://localhost:7085 (HTTP)

### =======================================
### 1. HEALTH CHECKS & STATUS
### =======================================

### Health Check Simples
GET https://localhost:7085/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Health Check Detalhado
GET https://localhost:7085/api/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Informaçőes do Sistema
GET https://localhost:7085/api/health/info
Accept: application/json

###

### Status do MinIO
GET https://localhost:7085/api/reports/minio/status
Accept: application/json

###

### =======================================
### 2. SIMULAÇŐES
### =======================================

### Informaçőes sobre Simulaçőes Disponíveis
GET https://localhost:7085/api/simulation/info
Accept: application/json

###

### Simulaçăo Rápida (5 pessoas, 2 empresas, 20 transaçőes)
POST https://localhost:7085/api/simulation/rapida
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Simulaçăo Completa Customizada
POST https://localhost:7085/api/simulation/completa
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantidadePessoas": 15,
  "quantidadeEmpresas": 8,
  "quantidadeTransacoes": 75
}

###

### Simulaçăo Intensiva (50 pessoas, 20 empresas, 200 transaçőes)
POST https://localhost:7085/api/simulation/intensiva
Content-Type: application/json

###

### =======================================
### 3. TRANSAÇŐES MANUAIS
### =======================================

### Solicitar Transaçăo Regular
POST https://localhost:7085/api/v2/transacoes/solicitar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tipoTransacao": "PIX",
  "valor": 1250.50,
  "moeda": "BRL",
  "contaOrigemId": 1001,
  "contaDestinoId": 1002,
  "descricao": "Transferęncia via PIX",
  "informacaoRemessa": "Pagamento de serviços"
}

###

### Solicitar Transaçăo TED
POST https://localhost:7085/api/v2/transacoes/solicitar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tipoTransacao": "TED",
  "valor": 7085.00,
  "moeda": "BRL",
  "contaOrigemId": 1001,
  "contaDestinoId": 1003,
  "descricao": "TED para outra conta",
  "codigoFinalidade": "OTHR",
  "nomeDevedor": "Joăo Silva",
  "nomeCredor": "Maria Santos"
}

###

### Transaçăo ISO20022 Completa
POST https://localhost:7085/api/v2/transacoes/simular-iso20022
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tipoTransacao": "PIX",
  "valor": 750.00,
  "moeda": "BRL",
  "contaOrigemId": 1001,
  "contaDestinoId": 1002,
  "informacaoRemessa": "Pagamento de fatura",
  "codigoFinalidade": "TRAD",
  "codigoCategoriaFinalidade": "OTHR",
  "descricao": "Transaçăo ISO20022 simulada",
  "nomeDevedor": "Joăo da Silva Santos",
  "contaDevedor": "237-1234-567890",
  "nomeCredor": "Maria Oliveira Lima",
  "contaCredor": "341-5678-123456",
  "bicAgenteDevedor": "BANK237BR",
  "bicAgenteCredor": "BANK341BR"
}

###

### =======================================
### 4. ENTIDADES - CRIAÇĂO MANUAL
### =======================================

### Criar Pessoa
POST https://localhost:7085/api/v2/transacoes/pessoas
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Joăo Silva Santos",
  "cpf": "12345678901",
  "rg": "12.345.678-9",
  "dataNascimento": "1985-03-15T00:00:00Z",
  "email": "joao.silva@email.com",
  "telefone": "(11) 3456-7890",
  "celular": "(11) 99876-5432",
  "enderecoId": null
}

###

### Criar Empresa
POST https://localhost:7085/api/v2/transacoes/empresas
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "razaoSocial": "Tech Solutions Brasil LTDA",
  "nomeFantasia": "Tech Solutions",
  "cnpj": "12345678000195",
  "inscricaoEstadual": "123.456.789.012",
  "inscricaoMunicipal": "12345678",
  "email": "contato@techsolutions.com.br",
  "telefone": "(11) 3456-7890",
  "website": "https://techsolutions.com.br",
  "enderecoId": null
}

###

### Criar Conta Bancária
POST https://localhost:7085/api/v2/transacoes/contas
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "banco": "237",
  "agencia": "1234",
  "numeroConta": "567890",
  "digitoVerificador": "1",
  "tipoConta": "ContaCorrente",
  "saldoInicial": 7085.00,
  "pessoaId": 1,
  "empresaId": null
}

###

### =======================================
### 5. RELATÓRIOS & MinIO
### =======================================

### Listar Resumos de Relatórios de Simulaçăo
GET https://localhost:7085/api/reports/summaries?limite=20
Accept: application/json

###

### Obter Relatório Específico
GET https://localhost:7085/api/reports/2024/12/24/simulation_report_20241224_143015.json
Accept: application/json

###

### Listar Todos os Arquivos no MinIO
GET https://localhost:7085/api/reports/files
Accept: application/json

###

### Listar Arquivos por Bucket
GET https://localhost:7085/api/reports/files?bucket=simulation-reports&prefix=reports/
Accept: application/json

###

### Listar Arquivos de Logs
GET https://localhost:7085/api/reports/files?bucket=banking-logs&prefix=2024/
Accept: application/json

###

### =======================================
### 6. DOWNLOAD DE ARQUIVOS
### =======================================

### Download Direto de Relatório
GET https://localhost:7085/api/reports/download/simulation-reports/reports%2F2024%2F12%2F24%2Fsimulation_report_20241224_143015.json
Accept: application/json

###

### Download de Arquivo de Log
GET https://localhost:7085/api/reports/download/banking-logs/logs%2F2024%2F12%2F24%2Fapplication.log
Accept: application/octet-stream

###

### =======================================
### 7. URLs PRÉ-ASSINADAS (ACESSO DIRETO)
### =======================================

### URL Pré-assinada para Relatório (60 minutos)
GET https://localhost:7085/api/reports/presigned-url/simulation-reports/reports%2F2024%2F12%2F24%2Fsimulation_report_20241224_143015.json?expiryMinutes=60
Accept: application/json

###

### URL Pré-assinada para Arquivo (30 minutos)
GET https://localhost:7085/api/reports/presigned-url/banking-exports/exports%2F2024%2F12%2F24%2Fdados_exportados.csv?expiryMinutes=30
Accept: application/json

###

### =======================================
### 8. UPLOAD DE ARQUIVOS
### =======================================

### Upload para Bucket de Relatórios
POST https://localhost:7085/api/reports/upload/simulation-reports
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

# Para testar via curl:
# curl -X POST "https://localhost:7085/api/reports/upload/simulation-reports" \
#   -F "file=@documento.pdf" \
#   -F "customFileName=relatorio-importante.pdf"

###

### Upload para Bucket de Exports
POST https://localhost:7085/api/reports/upload/banking-exports
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

# Para testar via curl:
# curl -X POST "https://localhost:7085/api/reports/upload/banking-exports" \
#   -F "file=@planilha.xlsx" \
#   -F "customFileName=dados_2024.xlsx"

###

### =======================================
### 9. REMOÇĂO DE ARQUIVOS
### =======================================

### Remover Arquivo do MinIO
DELETE https://localhost:7085/api/reports/simulation-reports/uploads%2F2024%2F12%2F24%2Farquivo_teste.pdf

###

### Remover Log Antigo
DELETE https://localhost:7085/api/reports/banking-logs/logs%2F2024%2F11%2F01%2Fapplication.log

###

### =======================================
### 10. CENÁRIOS DE TESTE COMBINADOS
### =======================================

### Cenário 1: Teste Completo de Simulaçăo
### Passo 1: Ver status antes da simulaçăo
GET https://localhost:7085/api/health

### Passo 2: Executar simulaçăo
POST https://localhost:7085/api/simulation/completa
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantidadePessoas": 10,
  "quantidadeEmpresas": 5,
  "quantidadeTransacoes": 30
}

### Passo 3: Aguardar uns segundos e listar relatórios gerados
GET https://localhost:7085/api/reports/summaries?limite=5

###

### Cenário 2: Transaçőes Manuais Diversas
### PIX
POST https://localhost:7085/api/v2/transacoes/solicitar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tipoTransacao": "PIX",
  "valor": 150.00,
  "moeda": "BRL",
  "contaOrigemId": 1,
  "contaDestinoId": 2,
  "descricao": "PIX teste"
}

### TED
