### Cenário 3: Gerenciamento de Arquivos
### Listar arquivos
GET https://localhost:7085/api/reports/files?bucket=simulation-reports

### Obter URL pré-assinada
GET https://localhost:7085/api/reports/presigned-url/simulation-reports/reports%2F2024%2F12%2F24%2Fsimulation_report_20241224_143015.json

